<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) The OHA has facilities for the receipt of transmissions via FAX, at FAX Number (202) 586&hyph;4972. 
