<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(c) The Department will evaluate each facility or service that meets the requirements of &sect;100.305 by the following
criteria to determine whether the facilities in the aggregate and the services in the aggregate are ``significant'':

